					"description": "[Cloudability Authentication](https://help.apptio.com/en-us/cloudability/api/v3/getting_started_with_the_cloudability.htm) follows a bearer token or \"Skeleton key\" format in which a key is provided on a user basis. This key is then used in tandem with basic autheticaiton formats to interact with Cloudability v3 Endpoints. _**It is important to understand that this method of authentication is soon to be depricated in favor of the more secure Frontdoor Authentication method.**_\n\nIn demonstrating this Authentication method we will be hitting the **Organizaitons Endpoint**. Information gathered from this endpoint are critical to understanding your organizational setting the most important of which is the Cloudability Organizaiton (Org) ID.\n\nThis Id (Example Below) will be used when requesting items from support against your Cloudability environment including the critical Refetch and Reprocess.\n\n<img src=\"https://content.pstmn.io/cf6bc2aa-2484-4c66-aea2-6ae9721065dc/aW1hZ2UucG5n\" width=\"706\" height=\"269\">"
