								"description": "**Ensure that the ending of this URL includes //**\n\n**In my endpoint above this is reflected as /cloudabilitysandbox.com/cs but will be different per customer.**\n\nEndFragment  \n\nThe environment id (apptio-current-environment) will be returned in the response body.\n\n<img src=\"https://content.pstmn.io/a0d9c8d9-76ec-460a-8b2d-2f3fc0495132/aW1hZ2UucG5n\" width=\"557\" height=\"240\">\n\nThis collection is setup to store this as a variable in your current Postman Environment via this test script:\n\n``` javascript\nvar jsonData = pm.response.json();\npm.environment.set(\"apptio-current-environment\", jsonData.id);\n\n```\n\n**This environment id will never change and only needs to be called once.**"
